/**
 * This file is .mjs because it is also imported by cli.mjs
 *
 * These settings are explicitly added to the config generated by the CLI. This
 * is because these settings are highly likely to be customized by the user.
 * Technically *any* setting can be customized by the user, but exposing these
 * makes the job that much easier and transparent.
 */

